{
  "stem": "5740.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A sample, only worse.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "With-- well, of no value.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of no value.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A sample of no value.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so because she had written sample, no value on the parcel--",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It came to me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A little bit of money sometimes and sometimes bread.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, in the, in the bread was a little bit of money sometimes.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But then, it was maybe 1943, and we knew that it-- we never-- I never knew about Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She didn't write much, but I only know that once our Lagerfuhrer was going to, to our city, to Sosnowitz, to the [NON-ENGLISH], and I promised her that my mother will give her lots of jewelry if she bring her with, with her to our camp.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You wanted the, the Lagerfuhrer, this Erma Hoffman--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Erma Hoffman to bring my mother to the camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And my mother didn't want to.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She said she's on a diet.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She can't be in the camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So you had an opportunity to bring your mother to you--",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she refused.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because the camp, that was the worst thing that, at this time, existed in my mother's--",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The thing, the thing that she knew about.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She was OK, but she suffered a lot.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was-- she wasn't a well person.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She always had severe arthritis, and she had kidney trouble and gall bladder trouble, all the Jewish troubles.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So you maintained this correspondence--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Till about August 1943.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In one of the last letters my mother wrote to me, I'm sending you a parcel.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And keep the box of the parcel.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She didn't say keep the box.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She said, I'm making a special box to send you a parcel.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then the parcel arrived.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I took whatever was in the parcel.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I threw the box out.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
